{"product_id":"linden-flower-conditioner-with-nordic-birch-extract-250ml","title":"Magrada Hair Stimulating Conditioner with Linden Flower Extract 250ml","description":"\u003cdiv class=\"entry-content\"\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https:\/\/www.magrada.eu\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/1-2-300x300.png\" alt=\"anne stiil ilulemmik 2019\" width=\"100\" height=\"100\"\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https:\/\/www.magrada.eu\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/2-2-300x300.png\" alt=\"iluteemant proff soovitab\" width=\"100\" height=\"100\"\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eEnjoy midsummer moments all year round. This conditioner is characterised by a composition of efficient Nordic plants which supports and accelerates natural hair growth. The silky, creamy composition of the conditioner spreads evenly on the hair, leaving behind a slightly honey-like aroma – like a warm July night.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe Nordic birch extract moisturises and softens the hair, making it easy to comb. The organic aloe extract has an calming effect on the scalp and prevents drying of the tips. The composition of plant extracts gives the hair a healthy shine, protects it from heat treatment, and preserves the pigmentation of the hair follicles, helping the hair to remain lively and elastic. The light conditioner is suitable for the entire family for daily use.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eNordic linden flower extract \u003c\/span\u003ehas a moisturising and softening effect suitable for a sensitive or irritated scalp.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eThe organic Nordic birch extract \u003c\/span\u003estimulates the circulation in the scalp and strengthens the roots, thereby accelerating natural hair growth.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eThe organic aloe extract \u003c\/span\u003ehas a deeply calming and moisturising effect on the skin. Aloe is well-known for its rich vitamin A, C, and E, folic acid, and collagen content.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/strong\u003e Apply the conditioner on your hair after shampooing, starting from the tips. Leave in for 2–3 minutes, then rinse with plenty of water. The conditioner is suitable for daily use.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eStore at a temperature of 5 to 25 degrees. When storing, protect from direct sunlight. Do not store the product near heaters or other heat sources.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e Aqua, Cetearyl Alcohol, Cetrimonium Chloride, Glycerin, Behentrimonium Methosulfate, Parfum, Cetyl Alcohol, Betula Alba (Birch) Leaf Exract*, Aloe Barbadensis (Aloe Vera) Extract*, Butylene Glycol, Alcohol, Tilia Cordata (Linden Flower) Extract, Phenoxyethanol, Ethylhexylglycerin, Potassium Sorbate, Sodium Benzoate, Hexyl Cinnamal, Geraniol\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e*COSMOS Certified Organic Ingredient\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eIngredients of natural origin: 92,77%.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe list of ingredients may be changed. Please see the packaging for the updated and most accurate list of ingredients.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eparaben-free \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e sulphate-free \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e silicone-free \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e vegan\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e | cruelty-free \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e hand-made \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e with a minimal list of ingredients\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e","brand":"Magrada Organic Cosmetics","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":48927685542215,"sku":"","price":12.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":false}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/magrada-hair-stimulating-conditioner-with-linden-flower-extract-250ml-1045756.png?v=1763665703","url":"https:\/\/bioskina.com\/products\/linden-flower-conditioner-with-nordic-birch-extract-250ml","provider":"bioskina","version":"1.0","type":"link"}